is also available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.colour-science.org/posts/colour-0312-colour-checker-detection-010/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (2 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>colour</category><category>colour - checker detection</category><category>colour science</category><category>release</category><guid>https://www.colour-science.org/posts/colour-0312-colour-checker-detection-010/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2019 03:47:21 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>